Challenge 16

Very simple, given an integer or a floating-point number, find its opposite.

Examples:

1: -1
14: -14
-34: 34


Answer:

function opposite(number) {
  if(number === -number) {
    return number
  } else if (number === number) {
    return -number
  }
}

