Challenge 46

Kids drink toddy.
Teens drink coke.
Young adults drink beer.
Adults drink whisky.
Make a function that receive age, and return what they drink.

Rules:

Children under 14 old.
Teens under 18 old.
Young under 21 old.
Adults have 21 or more.
Examples: (Input --> Output)

13 --> "drink toddy"
17 --> "drink coke"
18 --> "drink beer"
20 --> "drink beer"
30 --> "drink whisky"



Answer:

function peopleWithAgeDrink(old) {
  if (old < 14) {
    return 'drink toddy'
  } else if (old < 18) {
    return 'drink coke'
  } else if (old < 21) {
    return 'drink beer'
  } else {
    return 'drink whisky' 
  }
};

