Challenge 53

Complete the function that takes two integers (a, b, where a < b) and return an array of all integers between the input parameters, 
including them.

For example:

a = 1
b = 4
--> [1, 2, 3, 4]



Answer:

function between(a, b) {
  let arr = [];
  for (let i = a; i <= b; i++) {
    arr.push(i);
  }
  return arr;
};

